# Basketball Stats Keeper - General Rules

## Project Context
This is a basketball statistics tracking app built following the **FIBA Statisticians' Manual 2024**. The core goal is **speed** - capture any stat in under 2 seconds during live games.

## Key References
- Project Overview: @specs/overview.md
- Data Models: @specs/data-models.md
- FIBA Manual: specs/documents-corporate-fiba-statisticians-manual-2024.pdf

